						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Paridhāvin (1492 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of land in Pichchāṇḍārkōyil for offering of <hi rend="italic">musarōdaram</hi> (curd-rice) to the god in the name of Kōnēridēva-Mahārāja. The date <hi rend="bold">paridhāvin, Mārgaḻi 1,</hi> may be equated to <hi rend="bold">1492 A.D., November 27.</hi></p>						

